===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la}} {{term|Laconicus|Lacōnicus|Spartan}} < {{etyl|grc}} {{term|sc=polytonic|Λακωνικός|tr=Lakōnikos||Laconian}}. Laconia was the region surrounding and ruled by the Spartans, who were known for their brevity in speech.

